'''匈牙利邊界圍欄'''建於2015年，位於[[匈牙利|匈牙利]]與[[塞爾維亞|塞爾維亞]]和[[克羅地亞|克羅地亞]]接壤的邊界。匈牙利在[[歐洲移民危機|歐洲移民危機]]惡化後修建該圍欄，以加強邊境安全，阻止移民以非法途徑進入匈牙利，移民只能從邊境檢查站進入並需按照歐盟法律和國際法在匈牙利申請[[庇護權|庇護]]。<ref>[http://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-34260071 Migrant crisis: Hungary's closed border leaves many stranded] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-34260071 |date=20201223004227 }}. BBC News. 2015-09-15.</ref>邊界圍欄建成後，非法進入匈牙利的人數大減。<ref name="26 August 2016">[https://www.theguardian.com/world/2016/aug/26/hungarys-pm-plans-more-massive-fence-to-keep-out-migrants Hungary's PM plans 'more massive' fence to keep out migrants] {{Wayback|url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2016/aug/26/hungarys-pm-plans-more-massive-fence-to-keep-out-migrants |date=20210131081453 }}. theguardian.com. 2016-08-26.</ref>

在圍欄建成之前，進入匈牙利的[[非法移民|非法移民]]大多數並非以該國為終點站，而是計劃前往[[德國|德國]]等其它國家申請庇護，匈牙利只是他們旅程的一個中途站，因此不願意向匈牙利當局登記申請庇護，以免因《[[都柏林规则|都柏林规则]]》的規定而失去在其它國家的申請資格。<ref name="BBC 3 September 2015">[http://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-34136823 Migrant crisis 'a German problem' - Hungary's Orban] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-34136823 |date=20201108161136 }}. 2015-09-03.</ref>匈牙利－塞爾維亞邊界的圍欄於2015年9月建成。<ref>[http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-34250092 Refugees 'exhausted' after Serbia-Hungary border closes] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-34250092 |date=20170215104334 }}. BBC News. 2015-09-14.</ref>匈牙利後來也在與克羅地亞接壤邊界加建圍欄。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-34291648 |title=Migrant crisis: Neighbours squabble after Croatia U-turn |work=BBC News |date=2015-09-18 |accessdate=2016-10-02 |archive-date=2020-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108204729/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-34291648 }}</ref>

邊界圍欄的建造費用為2,700億[[匈牙利福林|福林]]（約等於8.832億歐元）。匈牙利政府於2017年要求歐盟分擔一半建造費用，<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.kormany.hu/en/the-prime-minister/news/it-is-high-time-for-european-solidarity-to-prevail-in-border-protection-as-well |title=It is high time for European solidarity to prevail in border protection as well |date=2017-09-01 |publisher=Press Office of the Prime Minister |access-date=2017-09-02 |archive-date=2019-09-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190922200929/https://www.kormany.hu/en/the-prime-minister/news/it-is-high-time-for-european-solidarity-to-prevail-in-border-protection-as-well }}</ref>被歐盟拒絕。

==塞爾維亞邊界==
匈塞邊界全長{{convert|175|km|mi}}。<ref name=BBCTroopPartol>{{cite news|title=Hungary sends police to deter migrants on Serbia border|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-33979648|publisher=BBC|date=2015-08-18|accessdate=2016-10-03|archive-date=2021-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125092440/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-33979648}}</ref><ref name=MarghitSecurity/>2015年6月，匈牙利內閣批准興建高4米的圍欄。<ref name=MarghitSecurity>{{cite news|last1=Feher|first1=Margit|title=Hungary Plans Security Fence on Serbia Border to Keep Out Migrants|url=http://www.wsj.com/articles/hungary-plans-security-fence-on-serbia-border-to-keep-out-migrants-1434561444|accessdate=2015-08-18|publisher=Wall Street Journal|date=2015-06-17|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108143226/https://www.wsj.com/articles/hungary-plans-security-fence-on-serbia-border-to-keep-out-migrants-1434561444}}</ref>工程於7月開始。<ref name=ConstrucitonBegins>{{cite news|title=Hungary Begins Building Serbia Border Fence to Curb Migrants|url=http://www.wsj.com/articles/hungary-begins-building-serbia-border-fence-to-curb-migrants-1436799052|accessdate=2015-08-18|agency=AP|publisher=Wall Street Journal|date=2015-07-13|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112020158/https://www.wsj.com/articles/hungary-begins-building-serbia-border-fence-to-curb-migrants-1436799052}}</ref>

圍欄於2015年9月落成後，那些不願意向匈牙利申請庇護的非法移民被迫改道進入[[克羅地亞|克羅地亞]]。<ref name=MullenCroatia>{{cite news|last1=Mullen|first1=Jethro|title=Migrant crisis: Thousands overwhelm Croatia|url=http://www.cnn.com/2015/09/17/world/europe-migrant-crisis/|accessdate=2015-09-17|publisher=CNN|date=2015-09-17|archive-date=2019-09-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190930115905/https://www.cnn.com/2015/09/17/world/europe-migrant-crisis/}}</ref>可是克羅地亞又把他們帶到與匈牙利接壤的邊境，於是匈牙利於2015年9月中在克羅地亞邊界加建圍欄。<ref name=dw_18.09.2015>{{cite news |title=Hungary starts building fence on Croatian border |url=http://www.dw.com/en/hungary-starts-building-fence-on-croatian-border/a-18721670 |accessdate=2015-09-18 |publisher=Deutsche Welle |date=2015-09-18 |archive-date=2015-09-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150920143401/http://www.dw.com/en/hungary-starts-building-fence-on-croatian-border/a-18721670 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2016年4月，匈牙利政府宣佈計劃加固圍欄。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.kormany.hu/en/ministry-of-defence/news/reinforcement-of-temporary-security-barrier-starts-on-the-hungarian-serbian-border |title=Reinforcement of temporary border barrier starts on the Hungarian–Serbian border |date=2016-04-04 |access-date=2016-10-02 |archive-date=2020-07-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200729115815/https://www.kormany.hu/en/ministry-of-defence/news/reinforcement-of-temporary-security-barrier-starts-on-the-hungarian-serbian-border }}</ref>

==克羅地亞邊界==
克羅地亞邊界的圍欄於2015年10月建成。<ref name=VOAclosingborderCroatia>{{cite news |title=Hungary to Close Border With Croatia |url=http://www.voanews.com/content/reu-migrant-shot-dead-trying-to-enter-bulgaria-says-ministry/3009905.html |accessdate=2015-10-16 |publisher=Voice of America |date=2015-10-16 |archive-date=2016-05-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160506045227/http://www.voanews.com/content/reu-migrant-shot-dead-trying-to-enter-bulgaria-says-ministry/3009905.html }}</ref>此後非法移民大多改為取道[[斯洛文尼亞|斯洛文尼亞]]北上。<ref name=SloveniaCroatia2>{{cite news |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2015/10/18/world/europe/hungary-closes-border-changing-refugees-path.html?hp&action=click&pgtype=Homepage&module=second-column-region&region=top-news&WT.nav=top-news |script-title=en:Hungary Closes Border, Changing Refugees’ Path |author=Barbara Surk and Stephen Castle |newspaper=The New York Times |date=2015-10-17 |accessdate=2015-10-17 |archive-date=2020-10-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201002090358/https://www.nytimes.com/2015/10/18/world/europe/hungary-closes-border-changing-refugees-path.html?hp&action=click&pgtype=Homepage&module=second-column-region&region=top-news&WT.nav=top-news }}</ref>

==立法==
2015年9月4日，[[匈牙利國會|匈牙利國會]]通過法案，把非法越過、破壞或阻撓建設邊界圍欄列為犯罪行為，新法律於9月15日起生效。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/world/2015-09/14/c_1116559886.htm |title=匈总理：从15日起非法入匈将是犯罪 |publisher=新華網 |date=2015-09-14 |accessdate=2016-10-05 |archive-date=2017-12-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171215221644/http://news.xinhuanet.com/world/2015-09/14/c_1116559886.htm }}</ref>

==成效==
在2015年9月的一個月內，共有138,396名非法移民進入匈牙利。圍欄建成後，2015年11月首2周每日平均只有15名非法移民被截獲。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.police.hu/hirek-es-informaciok/hatarinfo/elfogott-migransok-szama-lekerdezes?honap%5bvalue%5d%5byear%5d=2015&honap%5bvalue%5d%5bmonth%5d=11|title=Elfogott migránsok száma - dátum szerinti lekérdezés|website=A Magyar Rendőrség hivatalos honlapja|language=hu|access-date=2016-10-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170903025844/http://www.police.hu/hirek-es-informaciok/hatarinfo/elfogott-migransok-szama-lekerdezes?honap%5bvalue%5d%5byear%5d=2015&honap%5bvalue%5d%5bmonth%5d=11|archive-date=2017-09-03|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

